By April 2007 , Alice in Chains had been writing and demoing songs for the album , but the band did not show further signs of progress until October 2008 , when they announced that they had begun recording with producer Nick Raskulinecz in the studio .
They toured in 2006 , with William DuVall taking over as lead vocalist full-time .
The band reunited in 2005 for a live benefit show and toured in 2006 with William DuVall taking over as lead vocalist full-time .
The band toured in support of the album for two years before releasing the acoustic EP Sap in early 1992 .
The band has toured extensively and released several videos in support of these albums .
